Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.70,1:23:36.78,CN_Main,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.60,1:23:39.50,CN_Main,,0,0,0,,和我
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.86,1:23:44.36,CN_Main,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那個
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.75,1:23:47.96,CN_Main,,0,0,0,,我們一起來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.62,1:24:05.50,CN_Main,,0,0,0,,你能
